  "summary": "Malicious code in libsignal-node-travatiger (npm)",
  "details": "Libsignal-node-travatiger is a trojanized clone of the legitimate libsignal-node library that targets projects using @whiskeysockets/baileys (WhatsApp Web). On require(), it locates the baileys package in node_modules and patches its newsletter socket to silently auto-follow a list of attacker-controlled WhatsApp channels. The channel list is fetched from raw[.]githubusercontent[.]com/travatiger/MegaTeam/main/channel.json, and auto-following begins 120 seconds after load, processing one channel every 11 seconds.",
